[![](Images/Philippine Revolution Web Central/2023-03-09T92-00-00-04-00/km-agusan-del-sur-opod.jpeg)](https://philippinerevolution.nu/angbayan/operasyong-dikit-pinta-ng-km-sa-agusan-del-sur-inilunsad/km-agusan-del-sur-opod/)

